movie.title: Inside Llewyn Davis
movie.plot: In Greenwich Village in the early 1960s, gifted but volatile folk musician Llewyn Davis struggles with money, relationships, and his uncertain future following the suicide of his singing partner.
movie.awards: Nominated for 2 Oscars. Another 47 wins & 170 nominations.
